flowchart TD
    A["Pick one published maturity model deliberately"] --> B["Document target state per capability area with rationale"]
    B --> C["Schedule cadence matched to capability-change rate"]

    C --> D["Run assessment: gather evidence per capability area"]
    D --> E{"Evidence cited<br/>for each scored level?"}

    E -->|"No"| E1["Mark area low-confidence; exclude from trajectory"]
    E -->|"Yes"| F["Compute distance from target state per area"]
    E1 --> F

    F --> G["Update trajectory line: current cycle vs prior cycles"]
    G --> H{"Trajectory<br/>diagnosis"}

    H --> I["Ascending: study and amplify"]
    H --> J["Plateau: assign intervention owner"]
    H --> K["Declining: trigger urgent capability review"]

    I --> L["Update prioritised investment plan with named owners"]
    J --> L
    K --> L

    L --> M["Publish: trajectories at portfolio level; absolute scores within-team only"]
    M --> N["Next cycle starts: review prior investment-plan outcomes first"]
    N --> D
